  <itemBody>
    <div class="grid-row">
      <div class="col-12">
        <h4>You are well underway building the stage. The carpenters are making noise while building the stage, and therefore some of the guests are discontented. You have received this text message from John and Amy:<br/>
<img src="campingpladsen.png" alt="campingpladsen" width="32%"/></h4>
        <div>[Hello,</div>
        <div>It is so unsatisfactory for us to constantly listen to the noise from the construction work. It ruins our vacation. We wont some of our money back. Best regards, John and Amy]</div>
        <h6>You have written 5 possible answers to the text message. Chose the word that best describes each of the answers.</h6>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-row">
      <div class="col-12">
        <matchInteraction responseIdentifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" maxAssociations="0" minAssociations="0">
          <prompt/>
          <simpleMatchSet>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="choice_1" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="0" matchMin="0">Forthcoming</simpleAssociableChoice>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="choice_2" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="0" matchMin="0">Unsympathetic</simpleAssociableChoice>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="choice_5" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="0" matchMin="0">Sad</simpleAssociableChoice>
          </simpleMatchSet>
          <simpleMatchSet>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="choice_3" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="1" matchMin="0">
              <div>What did you expect? The construction work won't be over any faster, no matter how much you complain.</div>
            </simpleAssociableChoice>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="choice_4" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="1" matchMin="0">We are very sorry. Unfortunately, we cannot refund your payment, but we will try to ask the carpenters to make less noise during the construction.</simpleAssociableChoice>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="choice_6" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="1" matchMin="0">
              <div>You cannot get a return of your money. Construction work makes noise. You have to learn to live with it.</div>
            </simpleAssociableChoice>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="choice_7" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="1" matchMin="0">
              <div>Of course, that is not okay. We did hope that the construction work wouldn't be disturbing you as guests. But of course, it is our mistake. I am sorry!</div>
            </simpleAssociableChoice>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="choice_8" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="1" matchMin="0">
              <div>We are working on finishing the contruction work as fast as we can. As a compensation, we will offer you two nights stay for free.</div>
            </simpleAssociableChoice>
          </simpleMatchSet>
        </matchInteraction>
      </div>
    </div>
